name: To The Sky
description:
To The Sky is one of many artworks I made back when I was 12 years old, 6th June. 

I don't have anything to say. Using Photoshop CC that I got from my mom, I was trying to explore something that I found on the internet. So hope you like the very first artwork that I shared back when I was very young.

-Ridho (tandukuda)
